data.description: Expansive and stunning, this 4-bedroom Hidden Lakes home is a true masterpiece. The entrance leads to gleaming hardwood floors and vaulted ceilings, accentuating the spacious feel. A professional den/office adds functionality, while the Primary Suite is a haven with a 5-piece bath, soaking tub, French door entry, walk-in closet, and double sink with tiled backsplash.    The open floor plan is a marvel, featuring a loft and abundant natural light. The bedrooms are generously sized, with a formal living/dining room, a cozy gas fireplace, and a covered patio to amplify the charm. The large tandem 3-car garage offers convenience.    Seller Open to Buyer incentives!
